text: The 1989–90 North Carolina Tar Heels men's basketball team represented the University of North Carolina from Chapel Hill, North Carolina. Led by head coach Dean Smith, the Tar Heels reached the Sweet 16 in the NCAA Tournament. ==Roster== ==Schedule and results== |- !colspan=9| ACC Tournament |- !colspan=9| NCAA Tournament ==Rankings== ==References== Category:North Carolina Tar Heels men's basketball seasons Tar Tar North Carolina North Carolina
